			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="In this activity, the core team will finalize the details of a community engagement plan.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Bold"
			text="Why do this: ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="A community engagement plan helps you figure out how you're going to communicate and coordinate with community members. This planning process can help you expand your community network, enhance inclusion, and strengthen community buy-in and participation in next ERB activities.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Bold"
			text="How to do this: ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="Refer to the materials that you put together earlier in this chapter or existing community engagement materials you have. Use the table provided in the ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Hyperlink"
			text="Community Engagement Plan"
			linkType="externalDOC"
			link="Ch2_CommunityEngagement_Plan.docx">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text=" template to decide: the activities that are appropriate to communicate and reach your audience; how much time each activity will take; when you want to have them; venue; and how you will recruit.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
